An '''armored groundcar''' was a [[Groundcar/Legends|groundcar]] that had been modified or built with heavy armor for infantry transit and patrol in military situations. It was a cheap solution, however, as the maneuverability of wheeled vehicles was far inferior to that of their [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlift]] counterparts. On [[Haruun Kal/Legends|Haruun Kal]], armored groundcars were used by the [[Balawai]] [[Balawai militia|militia]] of [[Pelek Baw/Legends|Pelek Baw]].

